<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Your Review Has Been Published</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 700px; margin: auto; padding: 20px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
        <div style="border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; padding-bottom: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
            <h2 style="color: #00466a;"><%= appName %></h2>
        </div>

        <p style="font-size: 1.1em;">
            Hi <%= userName %>,
        </p>

        <p style="font-size: 1.1em; color: #28a745; font-weight: bold;">
            🎉 Great News! Your Review Has Been Published
        </p>

        <p style="font-size: 1em;">
            We're excited to inform you that the dispute regarding your review has been resolved in your favor. Your review is now published and visible to other users on our platform.
        </p>

        <div style="background-color: #d4edda; border-left: 4px solid #28a745; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px;">
            <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-weight: bold; color: #155724;">
                📝 Review Details:
            </p>
            <div style="color: #155724;">
                <p style="margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Product:</strong> <%= productName %></p>
                <p style="margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Review Title:</strong> "<%= reviewTitle %>"</p>
                <p style="margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Dispute ID:</strong> #<%= disputeId %></p>
                <p style="margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Resolved Date:</strong> <%= resolvedDate %></p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; border: 1px solid #dee2e6; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px;">
            <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-weight: bold; color: #495057;">
                📖 Your Published Review:
            </p>
            <div style="color: #6c757d; font-style: italic; padding: 10px; background-color: #fff; border-radius: 4px; border-left: 3px solid #00466a;">
                "<%= reviewContent %>"
            </div>
        </div>

        <div style="background-color: #e3f2fd; border-left: 4px solid #2196f3; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px;">
            <p style="margin: 0; color: #1565c0;">
                ✅ <strong>What this means:</strong> Your honest feedback is now helping other users make informed decisions about <%= productName %>. Thank you for contributing to our community!
            </p>
        </div>

        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
            <a href="<%= productUrl %>" style="display: inline-block; background-color: #00466a; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; padding: 12px 30px; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold;">
                View Your Review
            </a>
        </div>

        <p style="font-size: 1em; margin-top: 30px;">
            We appreciate your patience during the dispute resolution process and value your contribution to the <%= appName %> community.
        </p>

        <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #eee; margin: 30px 0;">

        <div style="color: #666; font-size: 0.9em;">
            <p style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                If you have any questions about this resolution or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.
            </p>
            
            <p style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                Best regards,<br>
                The <%= appName %> Team
            </p>
            
            <p style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                📧 <a href="mailto:<%= supportEmail %>" style="color: #00466a;"><%= supportEmail %></a>
            </p>
        </div>

        <div style="text-align: center; color: #999; font-size: 0.8em; margin-top: 40px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #eee;">
            <p>&copy; <%= currentYear %> <%= appName %>. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 